usions : We conclude that the hyperon content of neutron stars\nand supernova matter cannot be established with present constraints, and is\nessentially governed by the unconstrained coupling to the strange isoscalar\nmeson.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2016 21:39:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2017 10:46:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-09"}
