ize the empirical distribution of $\\{ \\log |V_n| -\n\\log |V_{n-1}| \\}$ prior to a large exceedance, showing that this distribution\nconverges to the stationary law of the exponentially-shifted Markov random\nwalk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2016 05:01:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-19"}
