tage of evolution compared to the secondary filament. The status and\nevolutionary phase of the Hi-GAL clumps would then appear to correlate with\nthat of the host filament.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2016 13:58:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-19"}
